  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h3>We offer a simple six-step programme designed to take all the pressure out of recruiting an apprentice as well as offering: </h3>
<ul>
<li>Free Organisational Needs Analysis to support your workforce development</li>
<li>Free Health &amp; Safety check</li>
<li>Excellent teaching and assessment</li>
<li>Use of college facilities</li>
<li>Flexible management and delivery of training</li>
<li>Apprentice progress reviews and our online assessment tool, Smart Assessor, so you can track your apprentice's progress at anytime</li>
<li>Help you with funding and paperwork.</li>
</ul>]]></mainContent>
