                          "subtitle": "5. Selection",
                          "description": "<p>You will select which candidates you wish to interview and we will liaise between all parties to support the interview. We will also help to arrange the interviews, notifying candidates of times and schedules. You will be contacted within 48 hours by your AEA after the interview to ask for feedback or selection decision.</p>"
